</b></p>
<p>172. At the 37th meeting, on 30 September 2011, the representatives of Bangladesh and 
the Philippines introduced draft resolution A/HRC/18/L.26/Rev.1, sponsored by 
Bangladesh and the Philippines and co-sponsored by Algeria, Benin, Djibouti, Indonesia, 
