<b>Independent Expert on the situation of human rights in C&#244;te d&#8217;Ivoire 
</b>Doudou Di&#232;ne (Senegal) 
<b>Working Group on human rights and transnational corporations and other business 
enterprises 
</b></p>
<p>Michael Addo (Ghana) 
